snippet.title: EAT GIRL trailer
snippet.description:
BUY FROM ITCH.IO ▶ https://tesselode.itch.io/eatgirl
TWITTER ▶ https://twitter.com/tesselode

EAT GIRL is a surreal top-down action game about moving through tight corridors and eating dots. You'll explore a world with strange creatures and varied ambient music. There are at least 20 levels, and skilled players can beat the game in around 2-3 hours.
